data.title: Libbioparser-dev
data.description: C++ library for parsing several formats in bioinformatics
data.name: bioparser

evidence: "Bioparser is a c++ header only parsing library for several bioinformatics formats (FASTA/Q, MHAP/PAF/SAM)" (a library intended to be included by other software).
Usage examples show inclusion via headers and templates, e.g. `#include "bioparser/fasta_parser.hpp"` and constructing parsers in user code, indicating it is a dependency library.

Installation/build instructions are via cloning and building the GitHub repository: `git clone https://github.com/rvaser/bioparser && cd bioparser` followed by CMake or Meson, with no mention of package managers or binaries.
